Package: ShowMeanField
Type: Package
Title: Mean-field Solver and Visualizer
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Adam", "Finnemann", email = "Adam.finnemann@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package solves and visualizes the solutions of the mean-fields of canonical statistical mechanics models including the Ising model, Blume-Capel model, Potts model, 0/1 Ising model, and continuous Ising model.
